## Changelog
### Features
* bbb451fa6b21f7fef0d82c58934cc15cb61bdb81 feat: Remove support for deprecated Hashicorp Vault Secrets
* 97d33b2e00939530054acd43d5125bd56df3c9cf feat: Add hardlink test to doctorcmd
* e6690ba087039582f97cbf448e8203238a0d3947 feat: Add --age-recipients-file flag to add command
* 79f3a3819f75b92d8e55b85a3ce843fbb9481060 feat: Add --age-recipient flag to add command
* f2ac4c841f305aa8455b136b111637846f6949cd feat: Add automatic Bitwarden CLI unlock
* bccf54287de502eb64b51ae9f85b037d4cdeb06d feat: Rename returnEmpty template function to abortEmpty
* 1fc3df8bb803cac65fb1b19bd70b0270cfa0f2be feat: Add returnEmpty template function
### Fixes
* 0994ed67d58261a748a7a905a7a3070aab698abf fix: Always use diff.pager if configured
* 3d64f508e33d2e6c435eeec397594b7e98d3fed1 fix: Use external diff tool for apply and re-add previews
* dbfced50a6a8c6472cd3c7091c2ec2740d2c3830 fix: Fix bad skip instruction in test script issue4479
### Documentation updates
* 9d0952f5b24ff10a5aeaa8a05e340b5815b0f170 docs: Add notes on edit watch and hardlink subtleties
* 59f19859b6381a601ec36a67abc556c3c7b88c18 docs: Add Beyond Compare merge tool configuration
* 3507963c4a6dab2ae8208176e35bdbc6d8a73a72 docs: Add lobste.rs links to social media
* d3d3c1200120038894c73b597a7a308ba2c29abc docs: Add link to article
